---
import CalButton from '../../CalButton.astro'
---

<section
  class='relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-32'
  style='background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 55% at 85% 10%, rgba(105,117,101,0.28) 0%, transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 0% 90%, rgba(105,117,101,0.22) 0%, transparent 45%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 35% at 50% 50%, rgba(236,223,204,0.35) 0%, transparent 60%),
    linear-gradient(148deg, #f8f4ec 0%, #ecdec6 35%, #dfd0b4 62%, #ece4d2 100%);'>

  <!-- Dot grid -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(24,28,20,0.045) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;'>
  </div>

  <!-- Edge vignette -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='background: radial-gradient(ellipse 100% 100% at 50% 50%, transparent 60%, rgba(24,28,20,0.04) 100%);'>
  </div>

  <!-- Watermark -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute -right-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 select-none overflow-hidden'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: clamp(12rem, 26vw, 22rem); color: rgba(24,28,20,0.035); line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap;'>
    SOLUCIÓN
  </div>

  <div class='relative mx-auto max-w-[1280px] px-5'>
    <div class='grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 xl:gap-24 items-start'>

      <!-- ── LEFT: Headline block ─────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class='lg:sticky lg:top-28'>
        <h2
          class='text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase mb-8'
          style='color: var(--color-sage);'>
          Contratar un consultor SEO
        </h2>

        <p
          data-animate
          class='font-heading text-h2 font-normal leading-[0.9] tracking-tight mb-1'
          style='color: var(--color-base);'>
          Pero se puede <span style='color: var(--color-sage);'>solucionar.</span>
        </p>

        <div data-animate class='mt-6 flex items-center'>
          <div
            class='h-px w-32'
            style='background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(105,117,101,0.08), rgba(105,117,101,0.45));'>
          </div>
          <div
            class='h-px w-10'
            style='background: rgba(105,117,101,0.65);'>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p
          data-animate
          class='mt-6 max-w-[40ch] text-base leading-relaxed text-pretty'
          style='color: var(--color-surface);'>
          En la llamada revisamos tu presencia en Google, analizamos a tu competencia y te digo exactamente qué está fallando y qué hay que hacer para que tus clientes te encuentren.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- ── RIGHT: 3-step process ────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class='flex flex-col'>

        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 py-10 border-b'
          style='border-color: rgba(24,28,20,0.1);'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span
              class='text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase leading-none mb-0.5'
              style='color: var(--color-sage);'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='text-h3 leading-none font-bold tabular-nums font-heading'
              style='color: var(--color-base);'>
              01
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p
              class='text-base font-bold mb-3'
              style='color: var(--color-base);'>
              Reserva tu llamada gratuita
            </p>
            <CalButton
              text='Agenda una llamada gratis'
              variant='cream'
              class='text-sm font-bold px-5 py-2.5'
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 py-10 border-b'
          style='border-color: rgba(24,28,20,0.1);'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span
              class='text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase leading-none mb-0.5'
              style='color: var(--color-sage);'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='text-h3 leading-none font-bold tabular-nums font-heading'
              style='color: var(--color-base);'>
              02
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p
              class='text-base font-bold mb-2'
              style='color: var(--color-base);'>
              Cuéntame tu situación
            </p>
            <p
              class='text-base leading-relaxed'
              style='color: var(--color-surface);'>
              Dime la dirección de tu web y qué te preocupa. Nada más.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 pt-10'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span
              class='text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase leading-none mb-0.5'
              style='color: var(--color-sage);'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='text-h3 leading-none font-bold tabular-nums font-heading'
              style='color: var(--color-base);'>
              03
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p
              class='text-base font-bold mb-2'
              style='color: var(--color-base);'>
              Hablamos 30 min
            </p>
            <p
              class='text-base leading-relaxed text-pretty'
              style='color: var(--color-surface);'>
              Reviso tu web en tiempo real, te explico qué está fallando y por qué Google no te muestra.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
